IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
    PROGRAM-ID. GOVERNED-PIPELINE.
ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
    OS "Linux".
    ARCH "x86_64".
DATA DIVISION.
    VAR input VIDEO-MP4.
    VAR output IMAGE-JPG.
    VAR log FINANCIAL-DECIMAL.
GOVERNANCE DIVISION.
    POLICY "no-tamper".
    REGULATION "SOC2".
    DATA-SOVEREIGNTY "EU" TO "EU".
    ACCESS-CONTROL "admin" ON "compress".
    AUDIT-LEDGER "start".
    DECISION-QUORUM "majority".
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    VALIDATE input "json".
    ENCRYPT input.
    AUDIT-LEDGER "encrypted".
    COMPRESS input.
    WRITE-FILE output input.
    CHECKPOINT log.
    AUDIT-LEDGER "end".
